Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.73,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good if yer always lookin' up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.55,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait patiently...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:15.36,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,And take it once it hits the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.74,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good to always be looking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.52,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Move patiently... at my own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:24.59,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If I practice calligraphy steadily, \Nwithout cutting corners on my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.54,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,then, in time, I may find my own style.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:29.92,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:32.38,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,Movie: Demon Geezer 2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:32.38,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of movie is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:35.72,MX Calligraphy 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Te~pid Tea \N\NMyopic Detective: Hot Springs Arc \N\NMovie: Demon Geezer 2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:35.72,MX Calligraphy 3,,0000,0000,0000,,OR Health Comes First\N\NExtra: \N250 Life Lessons Learned from Pandas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:35.72,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It was popular enough to get a sequel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:37.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:54.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:00:59.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:02.30,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:05.73,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt this island has a place \Nthat will fix computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:07.12,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Kawafuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:19.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:23.66,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't worked right since \NI dropped it in the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.64,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally busted completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:28.93,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No computer, no cell phone, no landline...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:34.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I contact anyone \Nfrom a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:52.69,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Barakamon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.96,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiman Ontsandon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.96,Barakamon Title Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Translation:\NIsland Dads
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:15.11,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A whole month has passed \Nsince I came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:20.47,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Contrary to the slow life I expected, \Nmy days are unexpectedly busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.36,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:27.22,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,there is one place that always heals my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.59,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:39.47,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is a paradise for cat lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.32,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.49,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to pet them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.62,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is someone else's property.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.70,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, come closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoo! Shoo! You filchin' felines!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn things broke into the fridge again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Landsakes, no need to get so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone'd be mad, if their \Nsashimi dinner got eaten up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sensei, you need somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:11.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you like cats, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come see 'em anytime you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Can I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:19.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all strays that settled \Nhere before I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, I won't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:30.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told ya, they're strays.\N They don't come near people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:32.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say so sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:34.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do with my arms now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:36.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We could tempt 'em with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:39.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stew left over from lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:40.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mere, Whitey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:44.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a bunch came over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the sashimi gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,those "leftovers from lunch"\N should be my dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a bunch came over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you named one "Whitey"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just call 'em that when I call 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just strays.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:02.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Society would consider these pet cats, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that tabby cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mere, Blackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "Tabby"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:13.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackie's the one that's closest to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The other strays won't let you pet 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:17.32,MX Main Dialog - down,,0000,0000,0000,,but Blackie's a smart cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.96,MX Signs - jp sub sub,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(190,1)}*Smart Cookie = Good Kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna hold one, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:27.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do! Please let me hold one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:30.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up an' take it! I can't hold it long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a bold grab!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then hold on tight with both hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.71,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:51.53,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a stray kitten is still cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told ya to hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:03.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you got a rash on yer neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:05.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:06.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:09.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes itch, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:13.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, think ya might be allergic to cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Allergic to cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:17.92,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.17,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:22.06,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't approach animals carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.07,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to be itchy, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:28.43,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, I can't take the itching from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can never have a cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:37.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would've known if I hadn't touched one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shopkeeper, the phone—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you come for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For shoppin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:51.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You kids are everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:55.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sensei, you got a rash on your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't remind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:58.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the shopkeeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to the senior center.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You may shop if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just need to borrow the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, d'ya know Akki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:10.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Akki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:13.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akki's amazin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's real good at video games!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like Master Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:27.42,MX Signs - jp sub sub,,0000,0000,0000,,Play For Just One Hour Each Day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.37,MX Main Dialog - down,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya don't know Master Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:27.42,MX Main Dialog - down,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Is he really that famous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:27.42,MX Signs - 16 Hits,,0000,0000,0000,,16 Hits
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a kyogen performer or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a master at video games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You need the telephone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.10,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Akki, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:40.10,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've seen him somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Tama's younger brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... yes, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:47.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you look so much like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a clone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop. We don't look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Genetics are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just hurry up and use the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It bothers you that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, it's black!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:01.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because it's a black telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only seen these on television.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:09.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In an era of cell phones with cameras and \Ntouch-sensitive screens, why is this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I scared ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:18.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be playing a game, \Nso help yourself to the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:25.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to make an important \Nphone call, so be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:26.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:28.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:32.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happens when I press it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this thing broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:37.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't press on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You turn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:41.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This black phone is just \Nstiff and hard to turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.58,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He blamed the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I turned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take yer finger out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}knew{\i0} that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:01.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work unless you pick \Nup the receiver before dialing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me the number you want to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dial it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you pity me, give me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:15.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, I'm on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kawafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds lively on your end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My computer broke, so I need to get a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get work without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About that, Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:36.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to take a break \Nfrom work for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:37.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Autumn's the deadline for the \NNaruka Institute Exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for you to be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As your friend, I thought I should look out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the date?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,September 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:54.07,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,41st Naruka Institute Calligraphy Exhibition
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:54.07,MX Handwritten - Naruka memo,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruka\NSept. 10\NHanda & \NKanzaki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:54.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can let it go this time \Nif you don't feel up to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you consider...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Order the writing equipment \NI'm about to describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I expect you to get the grand prize this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm in total darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll definitely find the light, someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:11.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:20.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the cost per minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Right now I'm in total darkness..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"But I'll definitely find the light."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was what I said that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:34.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In eighth grade, you claimed to harbor \Nsome power in your left arm, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's beside the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked for about five minutes, \Nso will fifty yen be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone costs ten yen per call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramma says to use it for free,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:50.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but everyone leaves ten yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:53.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here's ten yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this comes to forty yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:57.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:58.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:10:59.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:03.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you too, Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:10.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:12.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a nice, fat balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:14.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't touch it with your dirty hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:25.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd assumed that a calligrapher \Nwould be more stuffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would've known the \Ntruth if I hadn't met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an odd person, like they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come to visit sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:38.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean I'll have both siblings \Ncoming to trash my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:39.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:40.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't answer for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,None of this is good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:52.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't write anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:59.04,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because I stopped working \Nto focus on the exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:02.20,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing even a single sheet \Nfeels like a huge undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:05.20,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't improve my mood and \Nwrite something, the deadline—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you tryin' to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:12.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya spilled all the seaweed \NI worked hard to collect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I was lost in thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:17.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost in thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:20.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya expect to get off the hook \Nwith an excuse like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:22.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya think that's enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:23.84,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a gangster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:28.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't seen your face before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I moved in recently—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer the penmanship teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:34.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:38.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard yer an odd person, but a bad apple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:39.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Odd again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:45.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer gonna do me a little favor, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Where are we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forgot my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.50,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Caught by a Grade-A annoying old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do yer thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Write on it, real flashy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer outta luck, gettin' caught up with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After I told him 'bout you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:12.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he exclaimed, "I'll have \Nhim write my boat's name!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:14.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like he'd never forgive any failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:25.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad {\i1}is{\i0} mighty scary when he's mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the boat's name be \N"Miwa-maru," as the custom goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's a liquor seller. \NHe just bought the boat for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna give it my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.33,MX Signs - Registration,,0000,0000,0000,,Small Craft Registration Form
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.33,MX Signs - Registration 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Boat Name: {\fs26}Yuigadokuson-Maru \N{\fs20\i1}(I Alone Am Holy)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.33,MX Signs - Registration 3,,0000,0000,0000,,Owner: {\fs22}Yamamura Iwao
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Very unique taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad Mom picked my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "Yuigadokuson" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that I'm God, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:49.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.93,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely related...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.39,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Five kanji characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:55.50,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:59.06,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And with the curves of the hull, \Nit'll be hard to keep them balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.56,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,These aren't my usual tools, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.83,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Even discounting the pressure \Nhe's putting on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:06.87,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely can't afford to mess this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:08.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's paint!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The paint's gonna melt yer hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wash it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make a draft,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll go write it at home and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:27.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:35.43,MX Calligraphy - stencil,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuigadokuson-Maru
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:31.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll cut out the letters that I wrote,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:33.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll paint over the stencil...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hold on, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like all those other cookie-cutter boats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my boat to be one-of-a-kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:44.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but these aren't my usual writing tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:47.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's on something other than paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:49.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it done right, \Nyou should ask a specialist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:55.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, yer tellin' me to head out t'sea \Nin some ugly mass-produced boat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:59.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I mess up, it'll be ugly anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, yer gonna mess up, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't rule anything out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't nothin' to worry 'bout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:09.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get writin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can a pro really be turnin' down work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll{\i0} decide what's ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:20.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wanted to sail this out \Nwith print-out writin' on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have Naru do the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:29.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've... {\i1}sailed{\i0} in to the rescue! Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, it's time for yer liquor deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:33.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, just whip somethin' up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:34.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you sayin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:35.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whip something up"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.33,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,What d'you mean, "whip something up"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you always do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! A liquor seller's gotta sell liquor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.71,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "like I always do"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:49.01,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn gangster dad's got me cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:53.60,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm not one to back away from \Nanything after being talked to like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.83,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have him thanking me in tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:01.07,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That said, I really need to get \Nused to this kind of brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:05.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The paint won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hands'll melt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:07.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, it won't melt your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, is there anything \NI can use for test writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:16.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots of boards up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more than enough for test writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.15,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What were their names, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna write, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:37.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jacker Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:43.09,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm mostly used to this brush now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.10,Boards 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer Belly-Band Undersea Franken
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.80,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,My inner voice is really revealing itself, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:46.90,Boards 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gangster Dad                                      Demon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.65,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I have a feeling \NI can write decent calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:48.75,Boards 3,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuigadokuson-Maru (ha!) Gangster
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.65,Boards 4,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Geezer    Phantom Gangster
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:54.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:01.77,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait, I forgot to consider \Nthe curvature of the hull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.59,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.50,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll mess up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But now my neck hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad, but my neck hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to examine the hull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:17.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I nearly messed up, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this area looks good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't doin' nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:26.68,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.06,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I did all that test writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:32.78,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Faced with this pure white boat, \NI'm too scared to move the brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.60,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't I mess it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man... oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya better hurry before Miwa-nee gets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:43.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're distracting me! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared... I'm scared... I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he hates it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:50.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.99,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:56.08,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been under pressure before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.74,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It took a while before I \Ncould write something good,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.78,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,but I still pulled through when I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:03.93,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it just like then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:16.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:17.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you brats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you were sayin' you hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to cover up the handprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It splattered me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with it! I got splashed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to use strokes this bold \Nto cover up the handprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! Put ink in the bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:46.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:49.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, stay back so your \Nclothes don't get dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:53.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, put paper beneath wherever \Nthe ink's about to drip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:53.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.11,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.84,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared just a moment ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:01.72,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,but the pressure's completely gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.39,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and the brush is moving easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:08.45,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because of these little handprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! I'm running out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:14.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's havin' a lot of fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:16.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:21.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Village Chief said he's a guy \Nwho laughs while workin',
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,an' it looks to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:27.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take this seaweed as thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:32.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, isn't this the seaweed I just picked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:36.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call when it's launchin' time, \Nso you better come see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:42.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to be this happy with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:45.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm mighty glad I asked you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more {\i1}my{\i0} boat than I ever imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there's my hand—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:56.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was difficult to write calligraphy on a boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so it was good experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:01.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I thought of it as soiling white paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that made it easy to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you ever so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,for entrusting this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:10.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, setting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:15.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've amassed quite a lot of \Nresentment toward me, haven't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:23.45,Boards 5,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer Belly-Band Undersea Franken
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:23.45,Boards 6,,0000,0000,0000,,Gangster Dad                                          Demon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:23.45,Boards 7,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuigadokuson-Maru (ha!) Gangster
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:23.45,Boards 8,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Geezer    Phantom Gangster
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, those were...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:27.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those boards're meant for ferrying passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:29.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do 'bout this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away! Some adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, he dropped his seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, yer seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:39.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:40.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:18.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of trash around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:21.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, guys who come to fish \Nhere just toss stuff away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.53,0:22:22.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't heed warnings, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:26.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try putting up \Na well-phrased billboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:30.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Because of your littering, \Nthe world is coming to an end."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:33.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too large-scale. It doesn't feel realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't toss out trash, {\i1}you're{\i0} trash."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:37.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll rub them the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:38.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Litter and you'll die."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:39.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:42.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you think of one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:47.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Litter here, and you'll fester \Nwhere the sun doesn't shine."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:48.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dirty joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.68,MX Handwritten - on wood,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,900)}If you litter, all the crayfish will go away.
